POLYGON  Trademark Information
 POLYGON GLOBAL PARTNERS LLP
investment advisory services, investment management services and asset management services




Perfect for these industries

Insurance & Financial Services





Words that describe this mark
investment   advisory   services      investment   management   services   asset   management   services    
                                    




This is a brand page for the POLYGON trademark by POLYGON GLOBAL PARTNERS LLP 
                                in LONDON, , SW1X 9DQ.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this POLYGON trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner POLYGON GLOBAL PARTNERS LLP of the POLYGON trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the POLYGON trademark.
                           






On Tuesday, April 11, 2006,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        POLYGON by 
                        POLYGON GLOBAL PARTNERS LLP, LONDON SW1X 9DQ.
                        The USPTO has given the POLYGON 
                        trademark serial  number of  78859352.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED AND RENEWED.
                        The correspondent listed for POLYGON is 
                        
                        
                                            David C. Lee of 
                                            AKIN GUMP STRAUSS HAUER & FELD LLP,  1333 New Hampshire Avenue NW, Washington DC 20036 
                                .
                            The POLYGON trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for POLYGON 
                            is investment advisory services, investment management services and asset management services. 
                            





